data.text: @HighBleanBandB Husband and I both have it at the moment and I cannot wait to get out of the house. He’s on day 6 and I’m only on day 3. I want to wash everything in site and get all the windows open tomorrow.
@HighBleanBandB Glad you’re feeling better. I had a bout recently - can’t believe how exhausting it is!
@HighBleanBandB We are glad you are on the mend. ♥️
@HighBleanBandB I won’t ask if it knocked you for six.
@pitcarity A domino drive on 22nd February! I knew the risks but it turned out there were quite a few who were "recently" over covid. My high levels of Vitamin D intake did not actually help much!
@HighBleanBandB How did you manage to catch Covid way out there? Must have been some effort. Take it easy….
@HighBleanBandB Glad you're on the mend! Nothing better than a walk in the sunshine ☀
